      <description>&lt;h2 id=&#34;基础信息&#34; class=&#34;heading-element&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;基础信息&lt;/span&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;a href=&#34;#%e5%9f%ba%e7%a1%80%e4%bf%a1%e6%81%af&#34; class=&#34;heading-mark&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;svg class=&#34;octicon octicon-link&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 16 16&#34; version=&#34;1.1&#34; width=&#34;16&#34; height=&#34;16&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34;&gt;&lt;path d=&#34;m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z&#34;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;会议/期刊：Journal of Machine Learning Research 26 (2025), 1-51&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;关键词：Hopfield networks, associative memory, Fenchel-Young loss, sparse transformations, structured prediction&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;核心贡献&lt;/strong&gt;：本文提出 Hopfield-Fenchel-Young Networks，用两个 Fenchel-Young loss 的差构造统一能量框架，把 classical/modern Hopfield networks、sparse transformations、structured retrieval 和 post-transformations 纳入同一凸分析视角，并在多类记忆检索任务上验证稀疏与结构化检索能力。&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>论文 · MemGPT: Towards LLMs as Operating Systems</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/posts/%E8%AE%BA%E6%96%87%E9%98%85%E8%AF%BB-memgpttowards-llms-as-operating-systems/</link>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 Jul 2026 11:25:40 +0800</pubDate><author>ting10win@gmail.com (Ting)</author>
